{"tid":1058242,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有時夢境中既感覺會 帶埋出現實世界","createTime":"2019-03-12T11:49:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T14:36:40.000Z","uid":63626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6f968bbd3a8af72ce3f679acae23f600f4ff100d","tid":1058242,"uid":63626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T11:49:44.000Z","msg":"呢個夢我由細到大都有發過<br />\n夢既內容有時會唔記得，就算記得既都係發啲唔知做乜鳩既夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁呢個夢係有共同特徵<br />\n就係我每次訓醒，都會有種超唔舒服既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢樣都係我覺得困擾既地方<br />\n<br />\n一醒左之後會用比平時大既力度拎野，同時有種超執著既感覺，但完全唔知自己執著緊啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且極度不安<br />\n當我勁眼訓，想訓返個陣，呢種感覺又會再次襲來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近一次發到呢個夢個陣，一醒左之後就唔知點解要勁大力咁揸住部電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟住迫住自己係咁睇連登facebook,等呢種感覺散去先可以再訓返<br />\n<br />\n有冇人有類似經驗 或者可以幫忙解釋到呢個情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4ffdf90160496b2f452c6edfb3ea4341bd639f7","tid":1058242,"uid":124491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T11:54:44.000Z","msg":"問下李安納度"},{"pid":"888eedd5c54ac10245ec1e72fd0ce3811e92b6ee","tid":1058242,"uid":63626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4ffdf90160496b2f452c6edfb3ea4341bd639f7","tid":1058242,"uid":124491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T11:54:44.000Z","msg":"問下李安納度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T14:36:40.000Z","msg":"點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}